Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.88,0:07:40.95,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be20}麻婆豆腐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.57,0:13:01.78,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be20}老师的恩情  我永世难忘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.44,0:13:14.49,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be20}校园的景色  已印在心中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.31,0:13:27.68,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be20}回首看去  真是时光如梭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.19,0:13:39.33,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be20}临别之际  互道一…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.30,0:13:56.45,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be20}一声珍重
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.57,0:13:01.78,jap for AB,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be20}仰げばとうとし　我が師の恩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.44,0:13:14.49,jap for AB,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be20}教えの庭にも　はや幾年
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.31,0:13:27.68,jap for AB,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be20}思えばいと疾し　この年月
