Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.64,0:01:34.84,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)}三天之后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.01,0:01:53.86,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.27,0:01:56.87,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.74,0:01:58.35,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,保健室
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.27,0:02:00.27,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,保健室？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.50,0:02:04.39,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,你们为什么还在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.77,0:02:05.74,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,不要勉强自己
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.30,0:02:07.95,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,我没事的  小奏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.59,0:02:11.27,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这次对游离子你来说可真不容易
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.81,0:02:14.72,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,亏你这样还能担任战线的领袖到今天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.30,0:02:16.42,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,连你们也都还在…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.02,0:02:18.37,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,你们还留在这里干什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.08,0:02:20.63,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,影子不是已经消失了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.11,0:02:23.35,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就不会再有东西妨碍你们了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.59,0:02:24.80,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我们知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.42,0:02:26.11,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.63,0:02:28.88,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,可是你还留在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.13,0:02:31.23,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,你还留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.69,0:02:32.71,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.03,0:02:35.78,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.73,0:02:38.16,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,该说什么好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.85,0:02:39.35,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.08,0:02:41.34,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不太确定…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.97,0:02:44.52,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜由理所背负的纠葛或许已经解开了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.47,0:02:49.11,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吗  由理
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.10,0:01:31.10,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.87,0:02:53.48,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.01,0:02:56.31,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,好  就让我用催眠术来让你坦白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.31,0:02:58.40,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,少给我管闲事！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.14,0:03:01.09,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,从这抗拒的态度来看…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.27,0:03:02.36,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,说中了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.35,0:03:04.99,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,不…  没有这样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.59,0:03:06.62,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是领袖呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.74,0:03:09.26,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,这么容易就解开岂不惹人笑话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.40,0:03:09.91,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.96,0:03:12.12,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  就让我用催眠术…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.82,0:03:13.97,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  就是解开了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.05,0:03:15.52,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,有意见吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.72,0:03:16.79,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  承认了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.09,0:03:23.37,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,原来小奏这么坏心眼啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.85,0:03:25.66,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为由理太调皮了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.33,0:03:27.90,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,你还真能说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.90,0:03:31.05,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  我还真有点高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.94,0:03:32.60,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.24,0:03:34.64,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你能叫我由理
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.41,0:03:36.07,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.54,0:03:39.44,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,因为  这不就像是朋友一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.26,0:03:41.35,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.67,0:03:43.48,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.99,0:03:46.43,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,这么一来  我们的准备就不是白费力气了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.62,0:03:47.09,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.70,0:03:48.39,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,准备？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.93,0:03:50.04,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,要做什么事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.83,0:03:52.72,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,最后有件想做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.31,0:03:55.16,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,奏说她还没试过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.15,0:03:57.62,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？  是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.44,0:04:02.33,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,其他人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.73,0:04:03.58,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,都走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.19,0:04:05.72,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.41,0:04:08.11,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,全靠大家的帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.59,0:04:09.85,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然也花了不少力气
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.23,0:04:12.24,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,哼  那是神才做得到的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.14,0:04:14.80,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然嘴上诸多抱怨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.24,0:04:17.84,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,但大家其实都挺喜欢这里的生活呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.39,0:04:19.38,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,我总算是明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.99,0:04:22.02,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是托游离子的福呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.55,0:04:22.97,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.37,0:04:25.23,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  高松也走掉了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.66,0:04:28.19,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然变成NPC但后来恢复了意识
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.78,0:04:30.14,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.79,0:04:32.16,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,你看起来不太吃惊嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.16,0:04:35.54,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是说变成NPC以后就不能恢复过来了的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.64,0:04:38.10,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,看来是凭借坚强的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.21,0:04:40.86,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,就总有一天能恢复成人的设定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.95,0:04:47.06,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,这是哪首歌来着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.60,0:04:50.02,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才做准备时也一直在哼着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.02,0:04:52.13,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.94,0:04:53.95,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,是那首吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.35,0:04:56.66,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,岩泽同学最后唱的那首歌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.14,0:04:57.99,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,「My  Song」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.44,0:05:00.22,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,对  是那首歌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.86,0:05:04.08,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,通过全校广播放的那首吧  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.81,0:05:05.87,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,真是一首好歌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.52,0:05:06.94,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.29,0:05:10.95,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,体育馆？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.43,0:05:11.96,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.66,0:05:18.27,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}死后世界战线  毕业典礼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.28,0:05:21.58,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,我们几个人做的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.19,0:05:23.01,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,题字的是奏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.73,0:05:24.57,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.49,0:05:28.30,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,小奏  原来没参加过毕业典礼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.07,0:05:30.61,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,我想也许会挺有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.24,0:05:32.40,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,一点也不有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.83,0:05:35.90,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,不过写字的时候看上去挺高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.30,0:05:38.19,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,女生没几个是不哭的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.65,0:05:40.41,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,哼  所以说女人真麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.22,0:05:43.56,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.40,0:05:44.94,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,现在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.66,0:05:47.38,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为我们是为什么才换上这身衣服的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.72,0:05:48.59,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.95,0:05:50.82,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是在想真的会消失吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.54,0:05:52.87,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,我还没做好心理准备
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.31,0:05:55.67,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊  这样也算是原战线的领袖吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.11,0:05:56.74,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.38,0:06:01.25,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得自从大家消失之后  你就没了领袖的样子了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.22,0:06:03.03,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.64,0:06:05.40,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,这么一说还真有点变了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.38,0:06:06.81,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.41,0:06:08.15,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.57,0:06:10.64,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎更像一个女孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.81,0:06:15.70,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,我应该高兴  还是生气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.02,0:06:20.54,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗结束之后就变回连这种事情都不知道的纯真女孩了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.68,0:06:22.56,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,游离子也有可爱的地方嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.47,0:06:26.82,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋  笨蛋  笨蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.28,0:06:26.82,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}好痛好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.31,0:06:29.48,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,由理真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.73,0:06:31.95,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.83,0:06:34.73,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,会前致辞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.81,0:06:38.40,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,现开始举行一直在死后世界作战至今的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.67,0:06:41.74,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,死后世界战线的毕业典礼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.23,0:06:45.21,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,首先  齐唱战歌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.01,0:06:47.68,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,战歌!?  那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.50,0:06:50.08,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,死后世界战线的歌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.72,0:06:52.17,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,就当作是代替校歌的东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.97,0:06:55.42,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不记得让人编过这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.05,0:06:57.41,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,这歌也是奏编的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.77,0:06:58.90,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,是你编的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.31,0:07:01.80,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,话说你根本不是战线成员吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.02,0:07:02.97,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.44,0:07:04.69,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  把歌词发给大家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.66,0:07:06.42,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,曲调怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.31,0:07:09.30,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,校歌不都差不多吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.06,0:07:11.64,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,随便唱一下就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.31,0:07:12.61,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.10,0:07:15.16,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,预备
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.07,0:07:43.45,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,这歌词是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.60,0:07:46.13,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,谁事先检查一下呀  居然就直接唱了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.51,0:07:49.82,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,算了吧  小奏她也是花了不少心思才写出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.99,0:07:52.23,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,别这样说嘛  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.39,0:07:54.55,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,用心？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.06,0:07:57.57,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,这里不是写明了「随意」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.97,0:07:59.65,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,但是该怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.57,0:08:02.69,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,歌词里充满了奏的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.23,0:08:04.24,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.82,0:08:06.12,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,从头至尾全部
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.03,0:08:09.93,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.84,0:08:13.19,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了呢  小奏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.47,0:08:13.89,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.57,0:08:15.10,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.07,0:08:16.83,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.30,0:08:18.58,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,颁发毕业证书
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.15,0:08:19.73,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,有那种东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.26,0:08:21.15,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,特地做了的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.97,0:08:23.35,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然大部分又是让奏做的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.86,0:08:27.71,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,那么颁发证书的校长呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.07,0:08:28.92,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.66,0:08:37.98,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  我猜拳就是输掉了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.00,0:08:38.86,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,有意见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.42,0:08:40.91,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}仿佛就是为你量身定制的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.39,0:08:42.17,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  为什么总是我干这种苦差事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.24,0:08:43.35,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}那么  开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.47,0:08:52.67,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,颁发毕业证书
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.55,0:08:54.00,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.87,0:08:55.71,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,立华奏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.51,0:08:56.93,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.20,0:09:25.84,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来  仲村由理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.45,0:09:26.80,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.93,0:09:37.34,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,这打扮很适合你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.65,0:09:39.48,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,要你管
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.43,0:09:47.95,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.95,0:09:52.11,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来  直井文人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.69,0:09:53.08,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.57,0:09:57.78,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,赞颂我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.41,0:09:59.25,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.17,0:10:00.63,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.16,0:10:03.69,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢你所做的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.86,0:10:06.61,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,音无结弦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.46,0:10:07.90,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.39,0:10:14.05,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,把那个摘下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.45,0:10:16.15,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  那…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.54,0:10:18.47,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,日向秀树
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.66,0:10:21.18,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.93,0:10:24.85,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛  真是服了你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.08,0:10:27.83,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.48,0:10:30.45,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,我才是  受了你很多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.83,0:10:45.74,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,毕业生代表  致辞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.68,0:10:53.14,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,回首过去  发生了许多事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.57,0:10:58.74,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,在这个学校  我最先遇到的人是仲村由理同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.99,0:11:02.59,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,突然就被告知自己已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.96,0:11:07.40,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,并且得知留在这个死后世界的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.09,0:11:12.03,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都是不愿接受自己生前的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.65,0:11:14.41,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,对神做出反抗的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.33,0:11:17.33,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,我也作为其中的一员战斗过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.15,0:11:22.05,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我通过取回自己所失去的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.52,0:11:25.19,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,接受了自己的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.08,0:11:28.78,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,那是一份不可代替的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.60,0:11:33.61,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,于是我开始希望大家也能感受到同样的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.35,0:11:37.16,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都是一直抗争至今的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.26,0:11:40.95,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,这是件非常困难的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.03,0:11:47.52,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,但是他们能够互相帮助  互相信任
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.66,0:11:52.41,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,以仲村由理同学为中心组成的战线
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.99,0:11:55.39,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样的一群人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.82,0:11:59.11,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,将这份力量化为勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.36,0:12:02.69,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,大家渐渐开始接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.73,0:12:08.40,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,最后大家都积极向前…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.26,0:12:10.22,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,离开了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.82,0:12:14.04,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,留在这里的五人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.36,0:12:16.67,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,也将在今天毕业
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.05,0:12:21.73,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,即使忘记了一路走来的伙伴们的长相
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.20,0:12:27.37,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,也不会忘记这深刻在灵魂里的羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.45,0:12:29.52,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,能和大家一起度过这段时光
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.26,0:12:31.29,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,真的太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.92,0:12:33.89,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,太感谢你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.56,0:12:37.80,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,毕业生代表  音无结弦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.03,0:12:42.86,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,全体起立
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.27,0:12:46.66,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,齐唱「难忘您  恩师」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.74,0:13:40.44,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,唱慢了  你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.19,0:13:43.87,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,什么  明显是你唱快了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.11,0:13:45.72,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,是你太慢的缘故吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.46,0:13:48.95,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,对我和对音无就是不一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.38,0:13:46.26,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,我们唱得倒挺合拍的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.94,0:13:49.74,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,预备
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.67,0:14:14.46,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,闭幕致辞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.54,0:14:19.81,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,至此  死后世界战线的毕业典礼正式闭幕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.78,0:14:22.65,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,毕业生  退场
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.23,0:14:30.14,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不想看到女人哭成一片
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.66,0:14:31.24,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,先走一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.72,0:14:40.59,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,哭的人是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.73,0:14:43.43,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,音无同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.44,0:14:47.14,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,如果没有遇见音无同学的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.07,0:14:48.91,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.80,0:14:52.11,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,大概永远都得不到解脱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.48,0:14:56.03,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.35,0:14:59.38,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会再迷茫了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.77,0:15:02.07,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.05,0:15:05.77,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.56,0:15:10.42,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢…你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.03,0:15:17.01,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,走了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.41,0:15:21.17,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  接下来该谁哭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.42,0:15:22.79,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,谁会哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.75,0:15:25.41,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,小奏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.27,0:15:29.25,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,一直在和你争斗  真对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.77,0:15:32.76,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么没能早点成为朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.14,0:15:35.66,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,真的对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.74,0:15:37.38,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.85,0:15:39.81,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,我啊  是长女
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.19,0:15:44.20,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,一直代替父母照顾顽皮的弟弟妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.35,0:15:48.86,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,所以一定能教给小奏很多事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.74,0:15:51.82,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,小奏看起来是那么不知世故
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.22,0:15:53.84,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,让我特别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.80,0:15:57.29,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,明明能为你做好多事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.16,0:16:00.90,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,做好多事  一起玩耍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.61,0:16:05.83,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,要是  要是有更多一点的时间该多好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.12,0:16:09.67,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,该说再见了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.22,0:16:12.77,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.50,0:16:22.59,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,再见  小奏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.99,0:16:24.44,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.67,0:16:29.28,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.96,0:16:30.44,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.04,0:16:32.24,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你了  由理
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.26,0:16:34.65,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢你那么多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.99,0:16:36.90,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,头儿  辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.44,0:16:37.88,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.53,0:16:40.21,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  有缘再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.55,0:01:31.55,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,---
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.91,0:16:48.34,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来轮到我了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.50,0:16:50.19,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,按照顺序来看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.46,0:16:52.00,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我先走也可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.36,0:16:53.41,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.80,0:16:55.85,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,可别扔下小奏一个人自己先走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.60,0:16:57.52,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,我先走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.54,0:16:59.16,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.57,0:17:01.66,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.57,0:17:03.75,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,真谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.49,0:17:06.50,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,没有你的话什么都不会开始
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.32,0:17:09.28,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,也不会迎来这样的结局
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.85,0:17:10.58,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.43,0:17:12.29,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,只是碰巧而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.47,0:17:17.00,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,仔细一想的话  我本不应该来这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.78,0:17:18.73,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.53,0:17:23.27,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,我在死之前已经度过了一个释然的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.04,0:17:25.92,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那段记忆被封闭了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.34,0:17:27.95,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,我才误入了这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.66,0:17:29.78,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,因为想起了那段记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.38,0:17:33.96,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才能在这个世界里体会到释然的人生的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.05,0:17:36.47,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.37,0:17:40.29,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,你还真是个特别的存在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.12,0:17:46.37,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,所以能帮到大家也是多亏了这种碰巧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.20,0:17:47.85,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.04,0:17:50.84,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,说得太久也不好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.27,0:17:53.38,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.91,0:17:54.41,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.99,0:17:56.82,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,如果遇到了由依  也帮我向她打个招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.28,0:18:00.58,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,我应该攒了不少人品
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.09,0:18:02.61,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,我会尽情挥霍的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.74,0:18:07.31,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.61,0:18:11.95,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了  挚友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.89,0:18:21.62,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.56,0:18:23.64,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,毕业典礼感觉怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.92,0:18:25.78,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,开心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.43,0:18:28.02,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.15,0:18:31.38,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,但在最后很寂寞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.98,0:18:33.62,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这可是一个新的启程啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.09,0:18:37.86,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都向着新的人生出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.40,0:18:39.25,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,这是好事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.41,0:18:41.07,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.88,0:18:49.04,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  到外面去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.91,0:18:52.67,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,我想稍微吹一下风
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.89,0:18:56.30,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.81,0:19:09.01,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  奏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.17,0:19:12.35,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,要不一直留在这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.79,0:19:17.31,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,我突然想到的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.33,0:19:21.58,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,因为还会有像由理和日向他们那样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.11,0:19:25.90,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,人生没有得到释然的人到这里来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.75,0:19:27.57,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.62,0:19:32.69,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,他们说不定又会像由理他们一样留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.18,0:19:37.96,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里一直痛苦着  不停地反抗着人生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.29,0:19:39.03,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.74,0:19:40.53,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.21,0:19:42.73,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我们留下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.40,0:19:48.01,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,就可以像这次一样  把人生的美好传达给他们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.74,0:19:50.20,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,就可以让他们从这里毕业
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.07,0:19:56.04,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定我就是因为这个使命而来到这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.05,0:19:57.73,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.97,0:20:00.04,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,能和我一起留下来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.00,0:20:02.60,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,和奏在一起的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.33,0:20:07.02,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,即使是在这样的世界里  我也不会感到寂寞的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.10,0:20:09.37,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,我之前也说过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.37,0:20:11.79,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,我想和你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.59,0:20:14.44,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,今后也想和你一直都在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.18,0:20:17.00,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.37,0:20:21.33,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,是这么…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.39,0:20:23.06,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢奏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.50,0:20:27.04,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.67,0:20:35.18,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你一句话也不说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.12,0:20:37.04,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,不想说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.96,0:20:38.58,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.95,0:20:42.30,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我要是把现在的想法说出来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.08,0:20:45.18,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,我就会消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.42,0:20:47.10,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.29,0:20:53.21,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我是来向你说声「谢谢」的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.10,0:20:55.62,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.51,0:21:03.27,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我是靠你的心脏才活下来的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.63,0:21:10.29,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我的身体里  你的心脏在跳动着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.02,0:21:13.97,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,我唯一的不幸就是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.72,0:21:19.43,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,没能对赐予我青春的恩人说声谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.22,0:21:21.52,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,只是为了这句谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.16,0:21:23.81,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,只是为了这个心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.28,0:21:25.88,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,我才误入了这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.88,0:21:27.84,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.86,0:21:31.57,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,但你为什么会知道是我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.07,0:21:34.09,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,在一开始的那一刺时  我察觉到的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.82,0:21:37.38,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,你没有心脏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.36,0:21:41.07,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 只凭这一点…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.25,0:21:45.58,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,你之所以能取回自己的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.20,0:21:48.53,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为你在我的胸口上做了梦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.19,0:21:52.35,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为一直在听着自己心脏跳动的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.54,0:21:54.56,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.68,0:22:03.47,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,结弦  拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.01,0:22:09.40,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的那番话请再说一次
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.04,0:22:12.62,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.20,0:22:16.44,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,奏…会消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.80,0:22:17.45,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,结弦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.52,0:22:19.18,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.91,0:22:22.44,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事  我办不到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.88,0:22:23.58,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,结弦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.30,0:22:32.73,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,也请让我相信  你一直以来所相信的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.10,0:22:40.46,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,「活着是件很美好的事」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.38,0:22:46.90,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,结弦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.05,0:22:48.56,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,奏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.81,0:22:50.47,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.46,0:22:52.90,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,永远都和我在一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.39,0:22:57.22,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  谢谢你  结弦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.75,0:23:00.16,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,永远  永远都在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.21,0:23:03.22,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.03,0:23:04.72,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.52,0:23:06.20,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,奏
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.03,0:23:09.47,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  真是太感谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.33,0:23:11.53,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,奏
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.66,0:23:16.30,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你能爱我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.41,0:23:20.27,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,不要消失啊  奏
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.36,0:23:22.51,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,奏
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.55,0:23:24.84,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,赐予我生命
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.91,0:23:29.54,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,真的…很感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.85,0:23:50.02,chs for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,2000)}奏！
Comment: 0,0:01:30.00,0:01:30.00,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,---
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.64,0:01:34.84,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.01,0:01:53.86,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,ここは…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.27,0:01:56.87,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,どこ？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.74,0:01:58.35,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,保健室だ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.27,0:02:00.27,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,保健室？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.50,0:02:04.39,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,あなたたち どうしてまだいるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.77,0:02:05.74,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,無理しちゃダメ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.30,0:02:07.95,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,大丈夫よ 奏ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.59,0:02:11.27,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,まあ ゆりっぺにしちゃ大変だったようだしな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.81,0:02:14.72,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,よくそんなのでリーダーが務まっていたものだなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.30,0:02:16.42,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,あなたたちまで…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.02,0:02:18.37,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,いったい何してるのよ？　
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.08,0:02:20.63,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,影はもういないんじゃないの？　
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.11,0:02:23.35,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,なら邪魔するものは何もないはず
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.59,0:02:24.80,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,ああわかってる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.42,0:02:26.11,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,だったら…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.63,0:02:28.88,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,まだ お前が残ってるじゃないか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.13,0:02:31.23,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,お前が残ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.69,0:02:32.71,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,あ あたし？　
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.03,0:02:35.78,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,あっはは そっか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.73,0:02:38.16,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,何て言うんだろ…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.85,0:02:39.35,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,…何だよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.08,0:02:41.34,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,多分だけど…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.97,0:02:44.52,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,もうゆりの抱えてた葛藤は解けてる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.47,0:02:49.11,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,そうなのか　ゆり
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.10,0:01:31.10,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,えっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.87,0:02:53.48,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,えと…それは、その…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.01,0:02:56.31,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,よし僕が催眠術で吐かせて――
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.31,0:02:58.40,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,やめろコラァァー！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.14,0:03:01.09,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,と嫌がるということは…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.27,0:03:02.36,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,的中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.35,0:03:04.99,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,えっ？　あ いや そんなことないわ…ほら
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.59,0:03:06.62,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,ぁあたしリーダーなのに
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.74,0:03:09.26,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,そんな簡単に解けちゃってたら　いい笑い草じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.40,0:03:09.91,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,ね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.96,0:03:12.12,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,じゃあ　催眠術で…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.82,0:03:13.97,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,そうよ　解けたわよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.05,0:03:15.52,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,悪いかぁぁ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.72,0:03:16.79,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,あ 認めた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.09,0:03:23.37,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,奏ちゃん 意地悪なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.85,0:03:25.66,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,ゆりがあまのじゃくなだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.33,0:03:27.90,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,あなた 言うのね…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.90,0:03:31.05,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,でも なんとなく嬉しいな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.94,0:03:32.60,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,何が
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.24,0:03:34.64,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,ゆりって呼んでくれて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.41,0:03:36.07,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,どうして
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.54,0:03:39.44,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,だって…友達みたいじゃない？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.26,0:03:41.35,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,友達
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.67,0:03:43.48,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,そうね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.99,0:03:46.43,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,んじゃあ　準備は無駄にならなかったわけだな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.62,0:03:47.09,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.70,0:03:48.39,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,準備って
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.93,0:03:50.04,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,何か始まるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.83,0:03:52.72,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,最後にしたいことがあるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.31,0:03:55.16,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,奏 やったことないんだってさ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.15,0:03:57.62,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,え？　何を？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.44,0:04:02.33,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,他の皆は
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.73,0:04:03.58,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,全員いったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.19,0:04:05.72,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,そっか　良かった
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.41,0:04:08.11,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,皆が手伝ってくれたおかげだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.59,0:04:09.85,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,苦労はしたけどな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.23,0:04:12.24,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,ふん　神のなせる技だ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.14,0:04:14.80,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,でも 何だかんだ言って
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.24,0:04:17.84,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,皆けっこう楽しんでたんだよなここの暮らし
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.39,0:04:19.38,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,それがわかったぜ　
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.99,0:04:22.02,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,それも ゆりっぺのおかげだと思う
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.55,0:04:22.97,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,そう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.37,0:04:25.23,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,あぁ　高松もいけたんだぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.66,0:04:28.19,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,NPCになった後でも正気に戻れたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.78,0:04:30.14,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,へー　そうなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.79,0:04:32.16,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,あんま驚かないんだな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.16,0:04:35.54,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,NPCになったら戻れねぇって言ってなかったっけ？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.64,0:04:38.10,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,想いの強さで
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.21,0:04:40.86,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,いつか人に戻れるようにしてあったのね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.95,0:04:47.06,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,その歌なんだっけ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.60,0:04:50.02,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,さっき作業してる時も口ずさんでたよな？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.02,0:04:52.13,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,何だっけ？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.94,0:04:53.95,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,それあれよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.35,0:04:56.66,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,岩沢さんが最期に歌った歌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.14,0:04:57.99,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,　　
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.44,0:05:00.22,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,あああの曲か
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.86,0:05:04.08,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,全校放送で流れたやつだな　まったく
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.81,0:05:05.87,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,いい曲よね
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.52,0:05:06.94,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.29,0:05:10.95,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,体育館？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.43,0:05:11.96,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.66,0:05:18.27,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,　　
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.28,0:05:21.58,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,俺達で作ったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.19,0:05:23.01,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,文字は奏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.73,0:05:24.57,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,そうなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.49,0:05:28.30,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,奏ちゃん　卒業式したことなかったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.07,0:05:30.61,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,おもしろいのかなって
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.24,0:05:32.40,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,おもしろかねぇよぉ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.83,0:05:35.90,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,でも 字を書いてる時は 楽しそうだったけどな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.30,0:05:38.19,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,女子はたいてい泣くんだぜぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.65,0:05:40.41,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,ふん　これだから女は
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.22,0:05:43.56,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,じゃあ 始めよっか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.40,0:05:44.94,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,今から
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.66,0:05:47.38,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,何のために着替えたんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.72,0:05:48.59,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,ぁいや その
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.95,0:05:50.82,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,ホントに消えるのかなって
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.54,0:05:52.87,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,心の準備が…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.31,0:05:55.67,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,何だ　それでも元リーダか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.11,0:05:56.74,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,な 何よ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.38,0:06:01.25,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,お前 皆は消えたら　りーダーっぽくなくなったよな　なんか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.22,0:06:03.03,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,えっ そ そう？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.64,0:06:05.40,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,確かに何か変わったな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.38,0:06:06.81,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,えっ！どう？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.41,0:06:08.15,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,そうだなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.57,0:06:10.64,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,何か女の子っぽくなった
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.81,0:06:15.70,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,それ…喜べばいいの？怒ればいいの？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.02,0:06:20.54,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,戦い終えたら　そんなこともわからない無垢な女の子に戻っちまったんだな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.68,0:06:22.56,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,ゆりっぺも可愛いとこあんじゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.47,0:06:26.82,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,あぶ…あぶ あぶ あぶ あぶあばばばばば
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.28,0:06:26.82,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}なが！ったったいったい
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.31,0:06:29.48,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,ゆり面白いの
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.73,0:06:31.95,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,よし　始めるぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.83,0:06:34.73,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,開式の辞　
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.81,0:06:38.40,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,これより 死んだ世界で戦ってきた
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.67,0:06:41.74,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,死んだ世界戦線の卒業式を執り行います　
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.23,0:06:45.21,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,ではまず　戦歌斉唱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.01,0:06:47.68,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,戦歌！？　何それ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.50,0:06:50.08,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,死んだ世界戦線の歌だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.72,0:06:52.17,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,校歌の代わりみたいなもの
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.97,0:06:55.42,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,あたし そんなの作らせた憶えないわよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.05,0:06:57.41,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,それも奏が作った
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.77,0:06:58.90,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,あなたが作ったの？　
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.31,0:07:01.80,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,ってそもそも　あなた戦線じゃないじゃない！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.02,0:07:02.97,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,いいじゃねぇかはい
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.44,0:07:04.69,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,はい　歌詞回して
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.66,0:07:06.42,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,メロディーは？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.31,0:07:09.30,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,校歌って だいたい似たようなもんじゃん？　
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.06,0:07:11.64,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,適当に歌っとけば合うだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.31,0:07:12.61,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,では
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.10,0:07:15.16,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,せーのっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.07,0:07:43.45,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,って何だよこの歌詞！　
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.60,0:07:46.13,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,先に誰かチェックしとけよ　歌っちまっただろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.51,0:07:49.82,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,まあ　奏ちゃんなりに一生懸命真剣に書いたんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.99,0:07:52.23,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,そんなに言うことないじゃないねえ？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.39,0:07:54.55,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,「真剣に」って…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.06,0:07:57.57,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,「お気楽ナンバー」って堂々と書いてあるんだが
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.97,0:07:59.65,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,でも　何て言うんだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.57,0:08:02.69,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,奏の気持ちが詰まってる気がするよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.23,0:08:04.24,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,どこにだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.82,0:08:06.12,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,頭からケツまで
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.03,0:08:09.93,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,そうだな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.84,0:08:13.19,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,やったね　奏ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.47,0:08:13.89,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.57,0:08:15.10,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,次は
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.07,0:08:16.83,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,次は…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.30,0:08:18.58,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,卒業証書授与！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.15,0:08:19.73,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,あるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.26,0:08:21.15,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,作ったんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.97,0:08:23.35,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,また主に奏がな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.86,0:08:27.71,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,で　授与する校長は？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.07,0:08:28.92,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,俺だよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.66,0:08:37.98,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,クソォッ　俺がジャンケンで負けたんだよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.00,0:08:38.86,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,文句あっか！　
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.42,0:08:40.91,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}ふん貴様には適任だ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.39,0:08:42.17,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,クソ　何でいつも俺ばかりこんな役なんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.24,0:08:43.35,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}さあ…始めようぜ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.47,0:08:52.67,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,卒業証書授与
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.55,0:08:54.00,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,では…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.87,0:08:55.71,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,立華奏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.51,0:08:56.93,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.20,0:09:25.84,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,次　仲村ゆり
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.45,0:09:26.80,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.93,0:09:37.34,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,それ　似合ってるわよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.65,0:09:39.48,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,ほっとけ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.43,0:09:47.95,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,バカ…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.95,0:09:52.11,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,次　直井文人！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.69,0:09:53.08,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.57,0:09:57.78,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,我を称えよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.41,0:09:59.25,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,はぁー？　
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.17,0:10:00.63,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,ったく
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.16,0:10:03.69,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,お勉め　御苦労さまでした！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.86,0:10:06.61,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,音無結弦　
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.46,0:10:07.90,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.39,0:10:14.05,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,それ取れよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.45,0:10:16.15,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,ん　じゃあ…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.54,0:10:18.47,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,日向ひでき
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.66,0:10:21.18,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,あ はい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.93,0:10:24.85,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,何だよ　参ったな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.08,0:10:27.83,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,ありがとな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.48,0:10:30.45,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,こちらこそ　スゲー世話んなった
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.83,0:10:45.74,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,卒業生代表　答辞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.68,0:10:53.14,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,振り返ると　いろんなことがありました
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.57,0:10:58.74,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,この学校で　初めて出会ったのは　仲村ゆりさんでした
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.99,0:11:02.59,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,いきなり　死んだのよと説明されました
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.96,0:11:07.40,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,そして　この死後の世界に残っている人達は
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.09,0:11:12.03,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,皆一様に　自分の生きてきた人生を受け入れられず
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.65,0:11:14.41,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,神に抗っていることを知りました
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.33,0:11:17.33,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,私もその一員として戦いました
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.15,0:11:22.05,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,しかし　私は失っていた記憶を取り戻すことにより
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.52,0:11:25.19,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,自分の人生を受け入れることができました
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.08,0:11:28.78,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,それは…かけがえのない想いでした
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.60,0:11:33.61,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,それを皆にも　感じてほしいと思い始めました
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.35,0:11:37.16,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,ずっと抗ってきた彼らです
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.26,0:11:40.95,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,それはたいへん…難しいことです
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.03,0:11:47.52,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,でも彼らは…助け合うこと　信じあうことができたんです
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.66,0:11:52.41,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,仲村ゆりさんを中心にしてできあがった戦線は
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.99,0:11:55.39,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,そんな人達の集まりになっていたんです
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.82,0:11:59.11,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,その力を勇気に…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.36,0:12:02.69,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,皆は受け入れ始めました
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.73,0:12:08.40,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,皆…最期は前を見て…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.26,0:12:10.22,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,立ち去っていきました
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.82,0:12:14.04,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,ここに残る五名も
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.36,0:12:16.67,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,今日をもって卒業します
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.05,0:12:21.73,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,一緒に過ごした仲間の顔は忘れてしまっても
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.20,0:12:27.37,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,っ この…魂に刻み合った絆は忘れません
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.45,0:12:29.52,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,皆と過ごせて
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.26,0:12:31.29,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,本当に良かったです　
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.92,0:12:33.89,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,ありがとうございました
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.56,0:12:37.80,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,卒業生代表　音無結弦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.03,0:12:42.86,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,全員起立
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.27,0:12:46.66,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,「仰げば尊し」斉唱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.74,0:13:40.44,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,遅いぞ　貴様
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.19,0:13:43.87,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,何　明らかにてめぇが早かったろ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.11,0:13:45.72,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,貴様が遅いのが悪いんだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.46,0:13:48.95,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,あたしたちは合ってたわよね
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.38,0:13:46.26,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,ホンット音無の時と違うよなお前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.94,0:13:49.74,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,せーのっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.67,0:14:14.46,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,閉式の辞　
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.54,0:14:19.81,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,これをもって　死んだ世界戦線の卒業式を閉式と致します
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.78,0:14:22.65,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,卒業生 退場
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.23,0:14:30.14,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,女の泣き顔なんて見たくない
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.66,0:14:31.24,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,先に行く
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.72,0:14:40.59,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,おめぇが泣いてんじゃねぇかよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.73,0:14:43.43,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,音無さん…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.44,0:14:47.14,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,音無さんに出逢えてなかったら…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.07,0:14:48.91,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,僕は…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.80,0:14:52.11,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,ずっと報われなくて…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.48,0:14:56.03,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,でも…僕は
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.35,0:14:59.38,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,もう迷いません　
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.77,0:15:02.07,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,ありがとうございました
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.05,0:15:05.77,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,ああ…もういけ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.56,0:15:10.42,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,ありがとう…ございます
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.03,0:15:17.01,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,いったか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.41,0:15:21.17,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,さて 次は誰が泣く番だ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.42,0:15:22.79,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,泣きなんてしないわよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.75,0:15:25.41,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,奏ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.27,0:15:29.25,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,争ってばっかりで ごめんね
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.77,0:15:32.76,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,どうしてもっと早く友達になれなかったのかな…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.14,0:15:35.66,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,本当にごめんね
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.74,0:15:37.38,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,ううん
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.85,0:15:39.81,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,あたしね 長女でね
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.19,0:15:44.20,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,やんちゃな妹や弟を親代わりに面倒見てきたから
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.35,0:15:48.86,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,奏ちゃんにいろんなこと 教えてあげられたんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.74,0:15:51.82,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,奏ちゃん世間知らずっぽいから
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.22,0:15:53.84,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,余計に心配なんだよ？　
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.80,0:15:57.29,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,いろんなこと…できたのにね
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.16,0:16:00.90,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,いろんなことして　遊べたのにね
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.61,0:16:05.83,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,もっと　もっと時間があったらいいのにね
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.12,0:16:09.67,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,もうお別れだね
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.22,0:16:12.77,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.50,0:16:22.59,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,さようなら　奏ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.99,0:16:24.44,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.67,0:16:29.28,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,じゃあね
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.96,0:16:30.44,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.04,0:16:32.24,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,ああありがとな　ゆり
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.26,0:16:34.65,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,色々世話になりまくった
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.99,0:16:36.90,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,リーダー　お疲れさん
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.44,0:16:37.88,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.53,0:16:40.21,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,じゃあ　またどこかで！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.55,0:01:31.55,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,　　
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.91,0:16:48.34,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,ま俺だわな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.50,0:16:50.19,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,順番的に言って
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.46,0:16:52.00,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,いや　俺でもいいぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.36,0:16:53.41,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,何言ってんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.80,0:16:55.85,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,奏ちゃん残して先にいくなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.60,0:16:57.52,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,俺がいくって
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.54,0:16:59.16,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,そうか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.57,0:17:01.66,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,ああ　俺がいくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.57,0:17:03.75,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,色々ありがとな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.49,0:17:06.50,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,お前がいなけりゃ何も始まらなかったし
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.32,0:17:09.28,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,こんな終わりも迎えられなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.85,0:17:10.58,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,感謝してる
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.43,0:17:12.29,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,たまたまだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.47,0:17:17.00,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,よく考えたら　俺ここにくることはなかったんだよな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.78,0:17:18.73,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,どういうことだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.53,0:17:23.27,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,俺はちゃんと最後には報われた人生を送っていたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.04,0:17:25.92,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,その記憶が閉ざされていたから
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.34,0:17:27.95,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,この世界に迷い込んできた
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.66,0:17:29.78,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,それを思い出したから
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.38,0:17:33.96,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,報われた人生の気持ちを この世界で知ることができた
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.05,0:17:36.47,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,そうだったのか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.37,0:17:40.29,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,ホントに特別な存在だったんだな お前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.12,0:17:46.37,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,だから皆の力になれたのも　そういうたまたまのおかげなんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.20,0:17:47.85,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,そっか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.04,0:17:50.84,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,まあ長話もなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.27,0:17:53.38,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,じゃ　いくわ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.91,0:17:54.41,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.99,0:17:56.82,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,ああ会えたら ユイにもよろしく
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.28,0:18:00.58,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,おう運は残しまくってあるはずだからな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.09,0:18:02.61,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,使いまくってくるぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.74,0:18:07.31,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,おぅし
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.61,0:18:11.95,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,じゃあな　親友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.89,0:18:21.62,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,えーと…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.56,0:18:23.64,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,どうだった　卒業式　
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.92,0:18:25.78,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,楽しかったか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.43,0:18:28.02,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,うん　すごく
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.15,0:18:31.38,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,でも最後は淋しいのね
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.98,0:18:33.62,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,でも　旅立ちだぜ　
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.09,0:18:37.86,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,皆…新しい人生に向かって行ったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.40,0:18:39.25,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,いいことだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.41,0:18:41.07,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,そうね
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.88,0:18:49.04,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,あのさ　外に出ねぇ　
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.91,0:18:52.67,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,ちょっと…風に当たりたいかなって
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.89,0:18:56.30,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,ぁ…うん
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.81,0:19:09.01,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,あのさぁ　奏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.17,0:19:12.35,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,ここに…残らないか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.79,0:19:17.31,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,何か…急に思いついちまった
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.33,0:19:21.58,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,だってさ　またゆりや日向たちのように
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.11,0:19:25.90,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,報われない人生を送って　ここにきてしまう奴がいるってことじゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.75,0:19:27.57,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,そうね
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.62,0:19:32.69,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,そいつらまたゆりたちのように　ここに居着いちまいかねない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.18,0:19:37.96,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,ここでずっとさぁ苦しんで　生きることに抗い続けてしまうかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.29,0:19:39.03,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,そうね
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.74,0:19:40.53,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,でもさ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.21,0:19:42.73,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,俺たちが残っていたらさ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.40,0:19:48.01,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,そいつらに…今回のようにさ　生きることの良さを伝えてさ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.74,0:19:50.20,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,卒業させてやることができる
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.07,0:19:56.04,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,もしかしたら…そういう役目のために　俺はここにきたのかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.05,0:19:57.73,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,だからさ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.97,0:20:00.04,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,一緒に残らないか？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.00,0:20:02.60,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,奏がいてくれたらさ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.33,0:20:07.02,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,こんな世界でも　俺は…寂しくないから
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.10,0:20:09.37,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,前にも言ったかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.37,0:20:11.79,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,俺はお前と一緒にいたい
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.59,0:20:14.44,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,これから先も居続けたい
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.18,0:20:17.00,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,だって俺は
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.37,0:20:21.33,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,奏のことが　こんなにも
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.39,0:20:23.06,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,好きだから
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.50,0:20:27.04,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,好きだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.67,0:20:35.18,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,どうして…何も言ってくれないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.12,0:20:37.04,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,言いたくない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.96,0:20:38.58,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,どうして
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.95,0:20:42.30,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,今の想いを伝えてしまったら…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.08,0:20:45.18,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,私は　消えてしまうから
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.42,0:20:47.10,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,どうして
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.29,0:20:53.21,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,だって私は…ありがとうをあなたに言いに来たんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.10,0:20:55.62,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,どういうこと　だよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.51,0:21:03.27,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,あたしは…あなたの心臓で…生き永らえることができた女の子なの
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.63,0:21:10.29,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,今もあたしの胸では　あなたの心臓が鼓動を打っている
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.02,0:21:13.97,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,ただ一つのあたしの不幸は
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.72,0:21:19.43,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,あたしに青春をくれた恩人にありがとうを言えなかったこと
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.22,0:21:21.52,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,それを言いたくて…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.16,0:21:23.81,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,それだけが心残りで
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.28,0:21:25.88,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,この世界に迷い込んだの
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.88,0:21:27.84,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,そんな…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.86,0:21:31.57,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,でも　どうして俺だってわかった？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.07,0:21:34.09,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,最初の一刺しで気付けた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.82,0:21:37.38,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,あなたには…心臓がなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.36,0:21:41.07,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,でも　それだけじゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.25,0:21:45.58,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,あなたが記憶を取り戻せたのは
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.20,0:21:48.53,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,あたしの胸の上で夢を見たから
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.19,0:21:52.35,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,自分の鼓動の音を聞き続けていたから
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.54,0:21:54.56,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,そんな…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.68,0:22:03.47,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,結弦　お願い
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.01,0:22:09.40,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,さっきの言葉もう一度言って
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.04,0:22:12.62,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,そんな嫌だ…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.20,0:22:16.44,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,奏が消えてしまう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.80,0:22:17.45,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,結弦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.52,0:22:19.18,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,お願い
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.91,0:22:22.44,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,そんなこと　できない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.88,0:22:23.58,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,結弦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.30,0:22:32.73,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,あなたが信じてきたことをあたしにも信じさせて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.10,0:22:40.46,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,「生きることは素晴らしいんだ」って
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.38,0:22:46.90,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,結弦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.05,0:22:48.56,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,奏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.81,0:22:50.47,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,愛してる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.46,0:22:52.90,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,ずっと一緒にいよう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.39,0:22:57.22,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,うん　ありがとう　結弦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.75,0:23:00.16,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,ずっと　ずっと一緒にいよう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.21,0:23:03.22,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,うん　ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.03,0:23:04.72,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,愛してる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.52,0:23:06.20,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,奏
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.03,0:23:09.47,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,うん　すごくありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.33,0:23:11.53,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,奏
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.66,0:23:16.30,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,愛してくれて　ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.41,0:23:20.27,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,消えないでくれ　奏…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.36,0:23:22.51,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,奏…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.55,0:23:24.84,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,命をくれて…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.91,0:23:29.54,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,本当に…ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.85,0:23:50.02,jap for AB,NTP,0,0,0,,奏！
